data.description: This 1589 square foot single family home has 3 bedrooms and 2.0 bathrooms. This home is located at 598 Royal Dr, Jackson, MI 49202.
data.whatILove: Spacious, open living area. Beautiful hardwood floors downstairs. Newly remodeled bathrooms. Kinetico water softener. High efficiency furnace, and hot water heater. Partially fenced yard that is great for pets. Plenty of storage with additional 1 car garage attached behind the house and a lot of shelves in the basement as well as a new storage shed in the side yard. Feels private with pine trees surrounding the yard. Nice space to entertain both inside and out. Patio area just placed behind the garage next to the pool and additional patio area built on the west side of the house. Bonus space in basement and enclosed front porch. Close to I-94 and shopping. Northwest schools!
